Emanuel Levi Nau [assumed spelling].

01:21:59.280 --> 01:22:03.490
And I'm not applying this 20th
century idea to <i>The Merchant</i>

01:22:03.490 --> 01:22:08.870
<i>of Venice </i>, but what I am saying
