though a great deal becomes clear

01:22:13.390 --> 01:22:17.870
in the play, and so I think

01:22:17.870 --> 01:22:21.950
in that sense it's appropriate even
though the philosophy itself might

01:22:21.950 --> 01:22:24.880
not have been in existence
at that point.

01:22:24.880 --> 01:22:26.400
Shylock is fighting back

01:22:26.400 --> 01:22:30.520
against marginalization,
against this othering.

01:22:30.520 --> 01:22:34.090 position:56%
He fights back through his
negotiation of the bond with Antonio

01:22:34.090 --> 01:22:36.540
and through his conduct
during the trial.

01:22:36.540 --> 01:22:40.010
But he cannot overcome his
fundamental invisibility

01:22:40.010 --> 01:22:43.310
to the Christian forces
