charge us interest rates, et cetera.

01:52:24.940 --> 01:52:30.310 position:56%
So you -- it is a pleasure to be
able to borrow money that helps you.

01:52:30.310 --> 01:52:32.370
Returning money does not help you.

01:52:32.370 --> 01:52:34.310
So even if the Jews
are only paying --

01:52:34.310 --> 01:52:36.620
only charging decent
rates of interest,

01:52:36.620 --> 01:52:39.250
that leads to sentiments
against the Jews.

01:52:39.250 --> 01:52:42.010
That combines with
Christian anti-Judaism

01:52:42.010 --> 01:52:43.750
because their religion is off.

01:52:43.750 --> 01:52:48.460
Combines with the dislike
of the perceived oppressor

01:52:48.460 --> 01:52:51.990 position:56%
who is charging high interest rates,
et cetera, allegedly high rates.

01:52:51.990 --> 01:52:55.860 position:56%
But you have to return anything --
if you're borrowing, you need money.

01:52:55.860 --> 01:52:58.100
So returning more than
you borrow, returning --

01:52:58.100 --> 01:53:00.200
but borrowed is hard enough.

01:53:00.200 --> 01:53:03.870
Having to return interest
on top of it is even worse.

01:53:03.870 --> 01:53:07.990
That plus racial anti-Semitism
is another component.

01:53:07.990 --> 01:53:11.530
So that strengthens the
argument that the question is,

01:53:11.530 --> 01:53:15.170
